# match source files in subdirectories (e.g. templates/reviewer-prompt.md).
/EXPLORER_REPORT*.md
/DEVELOPER_REPORT*.md
/QA_REPORT*.md
/REVIEW*.md
/FINALIZE_REPORT*.md
/TASK.md
/AGENTS.md

